articles.title: Travis Kelce downs champagne while surrounded by women at Vegas club after leaving Taylor Swift in Australia - Page Six
articles.description: The athlete, who landed in Sin City Saturday morning after a whirlwind two-day trip to Australia, headed straight to LAVO where he celebrated at a party brunch.
articles.content:
Travis Kelce continued celebrating the Kansas City Chiefs Super Bowl win in Las Vegas over the weekend this time, without girlfriend Taylor Swift.
